article.headline: Matthews scores 14 as North Dakota defeats Waldorf College 87-36
article.description: — Brian Matthews scored 14 points as North Dakota beat Waldorf College 87-36 on Tuesday night.
article.linkText: Matthews scores 14 as North Dakota defeats Waldorf College 87-36
article.story: GRAND FORKS, N.D. -- — Brian Matthews scored 14 points as North Dakota beat Waldorf College 87-36 on Tuesday night. Matthews shot 6 of 8 from the field for the Fightin' Hawks (7-4). Treysen Eaglestaff scored 13 points while shooting 4 for 10, including 3 for 6 from beyond the arc. B.J. Omot shot 5 for 7, including 1 for 3 from beyond the arc to finish with 11 points. Justin Wiggins finished with 10 points, eight rebounds and two steals for the Warriors. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
